headline: 'Which series will win the Palme d'Or?': 'Twin Peaks' lauded at the world's temple of cinephilia
description: 'Breaking The Script' (5/5). In May 2017, the Cannes Film Festival screened the first two episodes of 'Twin Peaks,' season three. This celebration of David Lynch's cult series marked a definitive recognition of television fiction's artistic legitimacy.

description: While they still say they love their profession, teachers expressed growing fatigue in the face of overcrowded classrooms, ever-dwindling resources, and nonstop reforms that leave their jobs uncertain. As a result, many are considering leaving the field altogether.
